# Skills: Reusable Workflow Automation

## Skill Inventory

| Skill Name | Trigger | Tools Used | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| **git-workflow** | `/git-workflow` | Bash, Read | Structured commit, branch management, safe push |
| **experiment-scaffold** | `/experiment-scaffold` | Bash, Write | Auto-setup new experiment folder with README template |
| **test-writer** | `/test-writer` | Read, Write | Auto-generate unit tests based on function signatures |
| **validate-agent-config** | `/validate-agent-config` | Read, Glob, Grep | Validasi parity AGENTS.md vs agent definition files |
| **wiki-lint** | `/wiki-lint` | Read, Grep, Glob | Cek broken [[refs]], orphan files, missing front pages di .claude/wiki/ |
| **memory-promote** | `/memory-promote` | Read, Write, Bash | Promote memory entry dari project lokal ke parent workspace root |
| **knowledge-harvest** | `/knowledge-harvest` | Read, Write, Glob, Grep, Bash | Serap knowledge dari project AI agent lain ke wiki repo ini |
| **context-handoff** | `/context-handoff` | Read, Write, Bash | Simpan ringkasan session ke memory sebelum /compact agar findings tidak hilang |
| **stack-debug** | `/stack-debug` | Bash, Read, Grep | Health check web/mobile stack — status, ports, recent errors |
| **log-monitor** | `/log-monitor` | Bash, Read, Monitor | Stream log file realtime, filter pattern, stop on condition |
| **ui-test** | `/ui-test` | Chrome MCP, Read | Smoke test UI flow via browser, screenshot per step |

> Note: `stack-debug`, `log-monitor`, dan `ui-test` tersedia tergantung preset stack yang dipilih saat scaffold.
> Untuk preset `generic`, hanya 4 skill generik + wiki-lint + memory-promote + knowledge-harvest yang tersedia (semua universal — tidak bergantung stack).

---

## Decision Matrix

| Scenario | Skill |
|---|---|
| "I want to commit my changes cleanly" | **git-workflow** |
| "I'm starting a new experiment/feature" | **experiment-scaffold** |
| "I need unit tests for this function" | **test-writer** |
| "Saya baru edit agent rules, mau verify konsisten" | **validate-agent-config** |
| "Ada broken link di wiki atau file orphan?" | **wiki-lint** |
| "Mau promote lesson learned ke parent workspace" | **memory-promote** |
| "Cek semua service web stack masih berjalan?" | **stack-debug** |
| "Ada error di server, mau lihat log realtime" | **log-monitor** |
| "Test apakah UI login flow masih berfungsi?" | **ui-test** |
| "Mau serap knowledge dari project lama ke wiki" | **knowledge-harvest** |
| "Context hampir penuh, mau compact tapi jangan kehilangan progress" | **context-handoff** |

---

## Invocation Syntax

```
/git-workflow

Commit message: "refactor: simplify auth middleware"
```

```
/experiment-scaffold

Name: user-segmentation
```

```
/validate-agent-config
```

